LIBRO - END USER LICENSE AGREEMENT

Libro is provided to help manage library operations
including member management, book lending, attendance tracking, and reporting.

FEATURES INCLUDED:
- Member registration and management
- Book lending and return tracking
- Biometric attendance integration
- Payment and expenditure tracking
- Comprehensive reporting system
- Email notifications
- Data backup and restore

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
- Windows 10 or later (64-bit recommended)
- Minimum 4GB RAM
- 1GB free disk space
- Network connection for email features
- USB port for biometric device (optional)

SUPPORT:
For technical support and updates, please contact the developer or refer to
the documentation included with this software.

By installing this software, you agree to the terms stated above.